snippet.title: Improve unit testing with test doubles!
snippet.description:
Improve your testing strategy and accelerate development with Test Doubles. Discover how replacing real implementations with these test doubles helps you maintain a fast, reliable test suite, ensuring long-term productivity and enhancing code quality – see each technique, including their advantages and disadvantages to help you choose the right approach for your project.

Subscribe to Google for Developers → https://goo.gle/developers 

Speaker: Meghan Mehta
